OL,3,CThieves cause #30,000 of damage in
OL,4,Cdays of raids on scout hut
OL,6,FThieves caused more than #30,000 of
OL,7,Fdamage during a week of raids that
OL,8,Fleft a scout hut unusable, volunteers
OL,9,Fsay.
OL,11,FCopper piping was taken from Askern
OL,12,FScouts' building in Doncaster along
OL,13,Fwith heaters, tents, a barbecue and a
OL,14,Fflatpack kitchen which was due to be
OL,15,Finstalled.
OL,17,FSubstantial damage was caused to the
OL,18,Finterior after the burglars fell
OL,19,Fthrough the ceiling. They damaged two
OL,20,Fpizza ovens.
