OL,3,CThieves cause #30,000 of damage in
OL,4,Cdays of raids on scout hut
OL,6,FThe scout group only discovered the
OL,7,Fdamage on Monday, 9 September.
OL,9,FLead volunteer Matt Nicholls said the
OL,10,Fhut was left "unrecognisable".
OL,12,FHe said: "The burglars have been
OL,13,Fcoming back and forth over a seven-day
OL,14,Fperiod or more.
OL,16,F"They have taken copper out of the
OL,17,Fbuilding, wires, heaters, smashed
OL,18,Fbarbecues, stolen tents and pizza
OL,19,Fovens. It has been horrendous."
