OL,3,CThieves cause #30,000 of damage in
OL,4,Cdays of raids on scout hut
OL,6,FThe damage has meant the scout group
OL,7,Fhas been unable to meet.
OL,9,FMr Nicholls added: "The community are
OL,10,Fin uproar - they want the burglars
OL,11,Fcaught and the hut back up and
OL,12,Frunning."
OL,14,FEllie May Jackson has been attending
OL,15,FAskern Scouts since she was six years-
OL,16,Fold and is now a volunteer leader.
OL,18,FShe was among the group who discovered
OL,19,Fthe damage.
