OL,3,CThieves cause #30,000 of damage in
OL,4,Cdays of raids on scout hut
OL,6,FShe said: "Kids come every week to be
OL,7,Fsafe and have fun. It's all been
OL,8,Fruined and all the memories have been
OL,9,Ftaken away.
OL,11,F"My mum came here, my grandad came
OL,12,Fhere before her - it's a huge part of
OL,13,FAskern."
OL,15,FSouth Yorkshire Police have released a
OL,16,FCCTV image of three people they want
OL,17,Fto find.
