OL,3,CThieves cause #30,000 of damage in
OL,4,Cdays of raids on scout hut
OL,6,FPC Egan-Wyer, the officer in charge of
OL,7,Fthe case, said: "This Scout hut was
OL,8,Fthe fruition of ten years of local
OL,9,Ffundraising. We know how important it
OL,10,Fwas to the Askern community and the
OL,11,Famount of upset the incident has
OL,12,Fcaused.
OL,14,F"We are working hard to identify those
OL,15,Fresponsible and bring them to justice.
OL,16,FIf you know the people in the CCTV
OL,17,Fimage, please contact us as we believe
OL,18,Fthey may hold vital information which
OL,19,Fcould help our investigation."
